{"title":"MORALITY","sources":{"HDG.EC":[{"starred":false,"content":"could be that morality, w/ its visions of world order, is a monstrous offspring (<em>Ausgeburt</em>) of evil, & the much-appealed-to (<em>vielberufene</em>) <em>Weltöffentlichkeit </em>(word’s general public) remains in essence a construct (<em>Gebild</em>) and product (<em>Erzeugnis</em>) of devastation","locations":{"raw":"p. 135 ","list":[135],"high":135,"low":135},"source":{"display":"HDG.EC ","id":"HDG.EC","title":"Evening Conversation ","author":"HDG"},"motif":[{"name":"MORALITY","id":"morality","title":"MORALITY"},{"name":"ISLAMIC WORLD","id":"islamicworld","title":"ISLAMIC WORLD"},{"name":"EVIL","id":"evil","title":"EVIL"},{"name":"BEYOND ECONOMY / SURPLUS VALUE / GENERAL ECONOMY","id":"beyondeconomysurplusvaluegeneraleconomy","title":"BEYOND ECONOMY / SURPLUS VALUE / GENERAL ECONOMY"},{"name":"PUBLIC OPINION (SOCIAL MEDIA / PUBLISHING / TELEVISION)","id":"publicopinionsocialmediapublishingtelevision","title":"PUBLIC OPINION (SOCIAL MEDIA / PUBLISHING / TELEVISION)"},{"name":"REMAINDER / REMAINS / REMNANT","id":"remainderremainsremnant","title":"REMAINDER / REMAINS / REMNANT"}],"id":"HDG7","linkedContent":"could be that <a href='/motif/morality'>morality</a>, w/ its visions of <a href='/motif/islamicworld'>world</a> order, is a monstrous offspring (<em>Ausgeburt</em>) of <a href='/motif/evil'>evil</a>, & the much-appealed-to (<em>vielberufene</em>) <em>Weltöffentlichkeit </em>(word’s <a href='/motif/beyondeconomysurplusvaluegeneraleconomy'>general</a> <a href='/motif/publicopinionsocialmediapublishingtelevision'>public</a>) <a href='/motif/remainderremainsremnant'>remains</a> in essence a construct (<em>Gebild</em>) and product (<em>Erzeugnis</em>) of devastation"},{"starred":false,"content":"Nietzsche interpreted morality, the Platonic-Christian ethical doctrine, & its later secularized forms (rational Ethics of Enlightenment/socialism), as appearances (<em>Erscheinungen</em>) of will to p